underlying_goal: To fix a LaTeX formatting issue in a paper.
primary_success: Identifying and fixing a LaTeX formatting issue where probe questions were rendered as floating text by correctly wrapping them in an enumerated list within a quote block.
brief_summary: The user reported a formatting issue on pages 8 and 9 of a LaTeX paper. The agent identified that several lines of text were not properly formatted, wrapped them in a suitable environment, recompiled the paper, and pushed the fix.
